Limitation:
- lock screen orientation (fix is some kind of splash screen)
- push notifications (missing on iOS)
- only install in safari (which are pretty hidden, and not known to the public)
- missing popup hook for iOS app install
- transparency in statusbar (nice on pagescroll and full size images)
- vibration on iOS


